QuestData.Title: Life-Binder on Duty
QuestData.Description:
Soon the Life Pools will be full once again.
Thank you for your part in this, $n, it means more than I can ever hope to express.
Go, find the Life-Binder by the oathstone. Tell her that we are ready for the eggs.
QuestData.LogDescription: Meet Alexstrasza by the Ruby Oathstone.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Meet Alexstrasza by the Ruby Oathstone.
QuestData.RewardText: The future of all the flights is now secure.
